<div class="allianceSection collapsable collapsed">
	 <h4 class="header">Fire Characteristics</h4>
	<div class="text">Fluvial processes rather than fire primarily disturb stands of this alliance. Stands establish in areas directly after fires, such as in Anza-Borrego Desert State Park and adjacent San Felipe Valley. However, in other parts of its range, fire may be rare. The fire characteristics are little known for this alliance.</div>
